@Implementation
Reads the OpKind discriminant. Returns 1 if it falls in [6..12]
(MatrixMultiply, MatrixAdd, MatrixTranspose, MatrixInverse, VectorDot,
VectorCross, VectorNorm), 0 otherwise.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Pure read.
@End Security_Scope

